~ start
do change_background("test", "none", 0.0)
if GameManager.get_current_level_flag("mcbucket_zanopram_used") == true:
	=> sleeping_start
elif GameManager.get_current_level_flag("mcbucket_cannathink_used") == true:
	=> high_start
elif GameManager.get_current_level_flag("mcbucket_invigirol_used") == true or GameManager.get_current_level_flag("tv_turned_off") == true:
	=> invigirol_start
else:
	=> default_start
do change_background("test", "none", 0.0)
~ default_start
do show_cg("mcbucket_normal_base", "none", 0.0)
An ancient man stares at you intently.
Or at least, you think. The squint makes it hard to tell.
do SoundManager.play_music_track("mcbucket_normal_theme", 5.0)
What do you want to say to him?
~ default_hub
- Hey, how are you?
	The Old Man is still and silent.
	Then, almost instantly and possibly with intent to deafen, he screams:
	do show_cg("mcbucket_normal_ree")
	do SoundManager.play_sfx("mcbucket_scream")
	do shake(0.5, 20.0)
	Old Man: REEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE~~~~~!!!
	do GameManager.set_current_level_flag("mcbucket_has_screamed_at_player", true)
	do show_cg("mcbucket_normal_base")
	Wow, that was quite something. What do you wanna say to him?
	- What?
		do show_cg("mcbucket_normal_ree")
		do shake(0.5, 20.0)
		Old Man: REEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE~~~~~!!!
		do show_cg("mcbucket_normal_base")
		The Old Man seems to know only one response.
		What would you like to do?
		- Scream back at him
			That's it. Only one way to tell the bastard who's in charge.
			You put on your work face.
			Suck all the air you can in - into your stomach.
			You're gonna do it. Scream it back at him.
			3...2...1...
			do show_cg("mcbucket_normal_ree")
			do shake(0.5, 20.0)
			do SoundManager.play_sfx("mcbucket_scream")
			Old Man: REEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE~~~~~!!!
			do show_cg("mcbucket_normal_base")
			You let all that air out.
			Fucker beat you to it, it seems.
			~ ree_hub
			do show_cg("mcbucket_normal_ree")
			do shake(0.5, 20.0)
			Old Man: REEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE~~~~~!!!
			- REEEEEEEEEEE~~~~~!!! => ree_hub
			- Leave [Leave]
				"Goodbye Old Man" you say to the character in front of you.
				do SoundManager.fade_out_music(3.0)
				=> END
		- Leave [Leave]
			"Goodbye Old Man" you say to the character in front of you.
			do SoundManager.fade_out_music(3.0)
			=> END
